configuration/renderers.md
     1‚Üí# Configuring Renderers
     3‚ÜíRenderers (also called "backends") are responsible for creating the output of the book.
     4‚Üí
     5‚ÜíThe following backends are built-in:
     6‚Üí
     7‚Üí* [`html`](#html-renderer-options) --- This renders the book to HTML.
      ‚Üí‚Ä¶
    20‚Üí## Output tables
    22‚ÜíBackends can be added by including a `output` table in `book.toml` with the name of the backend.
      ‚Üí‚Ä¶
