     1‚Üí# Markdown
     3‚ÜímdBook's [parser](https://github.com/raphlinus/pulldown-cmark) adheres to the [CommonMark](https://commonmark.org/) specification with some extensions described below.
     4‚ÜíYou can take a quick [tutorial](https://commonmark.org/help/tutorial/),
     5‚Üíor [try out](https://spec.commonmark.org/dingus/) CommonMark in real time. A complete Markdown overview is out of scope for 
     6‚Üíthis documentation, but below is a high level overview of some of the basics. For a more in-depth experience, check out the
     7‚Üí[Markdown Guide](https://www.markdownguide.org).
