    82‚ÜíThe path to a static file.
    83‚ÜíIt implicitly includes `path_to_root`,
    84‚Üíand accounts for files that are renamed with a hash in their filename.
    85‚Üí
    86‚Üí```handlebars
      ‚Üí‚Ä¶
    90‚Üí### fa
    92‚ÜímdBook includes a copy of [Font Awesome Free's](https://fontawesome.com)
